Package: tPG
Type: Package
Title: Forecasting Recruitments via the Time-Dependent Poisson-Gamma Model
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Armando Turchetta <armando.turchetta@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Armando Turchetta <armando.turchetta@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains the functions needed to forecast recruitments in multicenter clinical studies via the time-depependent Poisson-Gamma (tPG) model (https://arxiv.org/abs/2301.03710). 
